  <intervention>
    <intervention_type>Other</intervention_type>
    <intervention_name>Test meal</intervention_name>
    <description>The two test meals are designed to have the same energy and macronutrient composition. They differ only in the carbohydrate source: fiber-enriched pasta or control pasta. Blood samples are taken at fasting and every 30 minutes over 4 hours. Fasting and postprandial intestinal fermentation is evaluated by breath test.</description>
